The use of semantic attributes for these tasks suggests that the paper belongs to the computer vision sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of machine learning techniques, such as transfer learning, which suggests that it may also belong to the sub-category of "cs.LG" (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of fashion photography datasets, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-category of "cs.MM" (Multimedia). The paper also deals with search and retrieval, which suggests that it may belong to the sub-categories of "cs.IR" (Information Retrieval) or "cs.CR" (Cryptography and Security).
